’Щ@d8c7f849a13d8f4a72f0e0312b2175261fa1202a4afbf2f8e8aba128d74c702fЪ&Title: title: grid
Path: Flags
Content:
``--width, -w {int}``
: Number of terminal columns wide (not output columns).
``--color, -c``
: Draw output with color.
``--icons, -i``
: Draw output with icons (assumes nerd font is used).
``--separator, -s {string}``
: Character to separate grid with.
